      "claim": "Retrospective clinical data suggests that patients with prior SARS-CoV-2 mRNA vaccination demonstrate improved survival outcomes when receiving ICI treatment.",
      "strength": "moderate",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "quote": "Retrospective human survival comparison p-value",
          "line_ref": "L30"
